<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA90">
<l>kūṟemakkī tentāy kuḷircaṭaiyai mītaḻittiṭ</l>
<l>ṭēṟa mikapperuki ṉeṉceyti - cīṟi</l>
<l>viḻittūrum vāḷaravum veṇmatiyu mīrttut</l>
<l>teḻittōṭuṅ kaṅkait tirai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tell us this, out father: what shall you do when it becomes very big</l>
<l>so that is rises, destroying on top [your] cool matted hair,</l>
<l>the waves of the Gaṅgā, along with dragging along [and] troubling</l>
<l>the hissing, looking, creeping bright snake and the white moon?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
